<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
		<title>EMA621_05_IH_0001</title>

		<!-- 공통 js-->
		<script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
		<script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

		<!-- 공통 css-->
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

		<!-- 개별 -->
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema621_05.css" />
	</head>

	<body>
		<div id="app_wrap" class="ema621_05_ih_0001">
			<section class="title type2">
				<h2 data-head="1" class="fraction_box_title">
					<div lang="y">
						딸기 3kg을 수확하는 데
						<div class="fraction_box">
							<span>3</span>
							<span>4</span>
						</div>
						시간이 걸렸습니다. 1시간 동안 수확할 수 있는 딸기는 몇 kg인지 구하려고 합니다. <span class="empty_box nemo"></span>안에 알맞은 수를 써넣으세요.
					</div>
				</h2>
			</section>

			<section class="contents">
				<div class="question_box dir_col gap_20">
					<div class="img">
						<img src="../../common_practice/img/EMA621_05_IH/0001_img.svg" alt="">
						<span class="txt1" lang="y">(시간)</span>
						<span class="txt2" lang="y">(시간)</span>
						<span class="txt3" lang="y">(시간)</span>
					</div>
					<div class="middle flex justify_end align_center">
						<div class="flex align_center">
							3÷
							<div class="input_wrap">
								<math-field data-answer-single="3"></math-field>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="flex align_center">
							(3÷
							<div class="input_wrap">
								<math-field data-answer-single="3"></math-field>
							</div>
							)×
							<div class="input_wrap">
								<math-field data-answer-single="4"></math-field>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="box_line">
						<div class="inner flex align_center">
							3÷
							<div class="fraction_box">
								<span>3</span>
								<span>4</span>
							</div>
							=(3÷3)×
							<div class="input_wrap">
								<math-field data-answer-single="4"></math-field>
							</div>
							=
							<div class="input_wrap">
								<math-field data-answer-single="4"></math-field>
							</div>
							(kg)
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				
				<!-- 해설 -->
				<div class="solve_area">
					<div class="inner_solve">
						<div class="flex">
							<strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
							<div class="conts_solve">
								<p>
								  <span class="fraction_box"><span>1</span><span>4</span></span> 시간 동안 수확할 수 있는 딸기의 양은 
								  <span class="fraction_box"><span>3</span><span>4</span></span>시간 동안 수확할 수 있는<br/> 딸기의 양을 3으로 나눈 것과 같으므로
								  3 ÷ 3 = 1 (kg)입니다.
								</p>
								<p class="gap_0 mt_20">
								  1시간 동안 수확할 수 있는 딸기의 양은 
								  <span class="fraction_box"><span>1</span><span>4</span></span>시간 동안 수확할 수 있는<br/> 딸기의 양을 4배 한 것과 같으므로 
								  1 × 4 = 4 (kg)입니다.
								</p>
								<p class="gap_0 mt_20">
								  ➔ 3 ÷ <span class="fraction_box"><span>3</span><span>4</span></span>
								  = (3 ÷ 3) × 4 = 4 (kg)
								</p>
							  </div>
						</div>
						<div class="buttons_solve">
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="btn_area">
					<button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
					<button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
					<button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
				</div>
			</section>
		</div>
	</body>
</html>
